references: Related: CF 264033. Amending: Ord 48022, Ord 91811. Repealing: Ord 97851.
summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to Dog and Cat Licenses, amending effective January 1, 1970, Section 95 of the License Code (Ordinance 48022) to eliminate the reduced fee as to certain applications, repealing Ordinance 97851 which amended said Section 95 of the License code, and re-enacting said section as if Ordinance 97851 had not been enacted.
